    "Empirical studies also show that calibrated imputation uncertainty enhances reliability in temporal clinical prediction and downstream ML pipelines [38], [39], [40].Our work complements these efforts by providing a unified, uncertainty-centric evaluation of classical, optimization-based, and deep generative imputers.",
